 True Corporation Logo
True Corporation Public Company Limited is a communications conglomerate in Thailand. True controls Thailand’s largest cable TV provider, TrueVisions, Thailand’s largest internet service provider True Internet and one of Thailand’s largest mobile operators, TrueMove H, which is second only to AIS having surpassed Dtac in January 2017. As of August 2014, True, along with True Telecommunications Growth Infrastructure Fund, had a combined market capitalization of US$10 billion. TrueMove is also a partner of Vodafone Group.
